 Searows 分享新单曲“I Have More Than Enough”并宣布推出 EP“End Of The World” https://www.nme.com/news/music/searows-shares-new-single-i-have-more-than-enough-end-of-the-world-3498201?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=searows-分享新的单身我已经足够了世界末日Anagricel DuranThu, 14 Sep 2023 20:40:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3498201 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="西罗斯。图片来源：马洛·奥斯塔拉" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “几周来第一次在外面散步后，我在一天内创作并录制了这首歌的大部分内容”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/searows-shares-new-single-i-have-more-than-enough-end-of-the-world-3498201">Searows 分享新单曲“I Have More Than Enough”并宣布 EP“End Of The World”</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="西罗斯。图片来源：马洛·奥斯塔拉" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Searows.-Credit-Marlowe-Ostara-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/searows">Searows</a>分享了他即将发行的 EP 《End Of The World》中的最新单曲《I Have More Than Enough》。</p><p>出生于肯塔基州、俄勒冈州长大的音乐家 Searows（真名 Alec Duckart）解释说，这首歌是在感觉缺乏灵感一段时间后一天写的。</p><p>他在一份新闻稿中说：“几周来第一次在外面散步后，我在一天内创作并录制了这首歌的大部分内容。” “我连续很多天独自在房间里创作歌曲，但我感觉越来越没有灵感。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Searows - 我已经足够了（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LqpNyBhVU50?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说道：“我绕着我的房子走了一圈，感觉很奇怪，然后我想起我可以在外面做同样的事情，所以我在我的邻居周围散步。我和几只猫坐在一起，看了一会儿乌鸦。</p><p> “我最终在回家的路上每隔几步就停下来，在我的笔记应用程序中写下随机的想法，当我回来时，我写了这首歌，然后将其录制下来。这是我写过的最快的歌曲之一，而且仍然感觉很好。令人震惊的是，走出去会让你感觉自己不再发疯了。”</p><p>他的 EP 《End Of The World》将于 11 月 10 日通过 Last Recordings On Earth 发行，这是<a href="/artists/matt-maltese">Matt Maltese</a>与 Communion Records 联合推出的新厂牌。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxI-pF4pwM4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: 